      <title outputclass="H4ForH3_1_9" class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">29.401-1</ph> Indefinite-delivery contracts for leased equipment.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p otherprops="Body"
            outputclass="Body"
            class="- topic/p "
            id="d1872e13">Insert the clause at <ph outputclass="ClauseProvisionXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="FAR-i1051445.dita#i1051445"
                     base="i1051445"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">52.229-1</xref>
            </ph>, State and Local Taxes, in solicitations and contracts for leased equipment when-</p>
         <ol class="- topic/ol " id="d1858e22">
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1872e26" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  A fixed-price indefinite-delivery contract is contemplated;</p>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1872e35" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  The contract will be performed wholly or partly in the United States or its outlying areas; and</p>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1872e44" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  The place or places of delivery are not known at the time of contracting.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
